      <details>
        <summary>What is Acrew Capital?</summary>
        <p>Acrew Capital is a multi-stage venture capital firm that invests in technology companies across sectors such as fintech, cybersecurity, data infrastructure, and consumer platforms. They are known for their thesis-driven approach and active operational support through their 'Crew' network.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
