      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What are some of Acrew's biggest investments?</summary>
        <p>Some of their most notable investments include Chime (fintech), Discord (communications), Plaid (financial infrastructure), and Figma (collaborative design).</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What is a 'multi-stage' venture capital firm?</summary>
        <p>A multi-stage firm invests in companies at various points in their lifecycle, from early seed rounds to late-stage growth rounds. This allows them to support founders throughout their journey and continually inject capital into their most successful portfolio companies.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How can following VC portfolios help my investing?</summary>
        <p>Tracking VC investments helps you identify emerging macroeconomic trends before they hit the mainstream, discover future IPO candidates, and understand the competitive landscape facing established, publicly traded companies in your current portfolio.</p>
      </details>

    </section>
